accordionDescriptionText: Submit your NAAAR when (1) your state enters contract with a new managed care plan or (2) there are any significant changes to a Managed Care Organization (MCO), Prepaid Inpatient Health Plan (PIHP) or Prepaid Ambulatory Health Plan (PAHP) operation such as:
accordionDescriptionTextBulletTwo: Changes to services, benefits, geographic service area, composition of provider network or payments to its provider network
